@startuml REQ-0011 Humidity Sensing
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
  participant "Controller" as Controller
end box

header
  **REQ-0011: Humidity Sensing**
  //Description:// Read raw humidity values from the ADC hardware interface and\npost sensor data events for downstream processing.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Sensor_ReadHumidity returns valid ADC reading.\nEVENT_SENSOR_DATA_READY posted with raw value.
end header


== Sensor_ReadHumidity() ==
Sensor_Driver --> Controller: EVENT_SENSOR_DATA_READY\nSensor_ReadHumidity() -> Controller_OnSensorData()
note right of Controller: Threshold Check
alt sensor_value > threshold
Controller --> Controller: EVENT_CONTROL_ACTION\nController_OnSensorData() -> Controller_ReportStatus()
end alt

@enduml